## Third-Party Data Notice

This repository's CODE and ONTOLOGY STRUCTURE are MIT-licensed, but does NOT
bundle or redistribute the full text of the following referenced works. Their
original content remains under their respective copyright holders:

- KCS/KDS (Korean Construction Specifications/Standards)
  Copyright: Ministry of Land, Infrastructure and Transport / Korea
  Construction Standards Center (kcsc.re.kr)
  License: Korea Open Government License (공공누리) Type 2 — attribution,
  no modification/redistribution of original text.

- Quality Management Guidelines for Construction Works
  Copyright: Ministry of Land, Infrastructure and Transport (notice).

- KS (Korean Industrial Standards)
  Copyright: Korean Agency for Technology and Standards / KSA.
  License: Commercial license required for original text.

Users who need original clause text must obtain it from the respective
agencies. This server's RAG features (Phase 2+) operate on user-supplied
documents only; no original standard text is distributed via npm or GitHub.
